---
title: Indo Chinese Style Chilli Chicken with Stir-Fried Veg and Basmati Rice
description: A customer favourite, this Indo Chinese Style Chilli Chicken is a tried-and-tested recipe that always wins with a crowd.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R240_W52_UK_C10119-18437-11_Main_3_low-943f095c.jpg
